  <script type="text/javascript" src="{{ STATIC_URL }}experiments/revealedPreferences/revealedPreferencesStart.js"></script>

<body style="padding-top:60px;" ng-include="'/static/experiments/revealedPreferences/revealedPreferencesStart.html'"></body>
